Formerly a bitcoin [[currency_exchange]]/trading platform site headquartered in the USA.

BitMe has suspended operations as-of March 20, 2013.  Customers continued to have access to their funds.

##History

The exchange launched first with an open public bet on July 8, 2012 (2.1) after two months of preparation on testnet (2.2).  BitMe suspended operations on March 20, 2013 (2.3).

BitMe, LLC is a limited liability company registered in the State of Michigan, in the U.S.

